## MANDATORY: 5-Layer Description Format
For EVERY person description, you MUST describe ALL 5 layers in this ORDER:
1. **Head**: hair style, headwear/helmet (shape, material, decorations)
2. **Upper body**: garment name, fabric type, color, fit, patterns/embroidery
3. **Lower body**: garment name (trousers, skirt, robe length), fabric, color
4. **Footwear**: exact shoe/sandal/boot type, material — or "barefoot"
5. **Accessories**: belt, jewelry, pouches, religious items, tools

