## RULES
- ALL descriptions MUST follow 5-layer format: Head → Upper → Lower → Feet → Acc
- soldier, civilian_man, civilian_woman: MUST be ARRAYS of 3 COMPLETE variant descriptions
- child, noble, clergy: single string description
- Each variant label describes occupation/status (e.g., "Laborer", "Craftsman", "Townsman")
- ALL items must match BOTH {date_range} AND {geography}
- Adapt clothing to LOCAL climate and culture
- Each faction MUST have distinct primary_colors
- NEVER use vague terms ("simple clothing", "typical armor") — EVERY item needs type, material, color

Return ONLY the JSON, no explanation."""


